quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,1,"O you who covers himself [with a garment],<sup foot_note=197644>1</sup>",footnotes:197644:1
  74,2,"Arise and warn."
  74,3,"And your Lord glorify."
  74,4,"And your clothing purify."
  74,5,"And uncleanliness<sup foot_note=197645>1</sup> avoid.",footnotes:197645:1
  74,6,"And do not confer favor to acquire more<sup foot_note=197646>1</sup>.",footnotes:197646:1
  74,7,"But for your Lord be patient."
  74,8,"And when the trumpet is blown,"
  74,9,"That Day will be a difficult day"
  74,10,"For the disbelievers - not easy."